cetus.hir

Class DepthFirstIterator<E extends Traversable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.IRIterator<E>
      • cetus.hir.DepthFirstIterator<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<E>

    public class DepthFirstIterator<E extends Traversable>
extends IRIterator<E>
    Iterates over Traversable objects in depth-first order. The iteration starts from the root object that was specified in the constructor.
